  "text": "According to [CITATION_1] Lemma 4.4] , every cuspidal perverse sheaf on g is in fact supported on N G . (Here, we are using the assumption that g is semisimple.) Since the Fourier-Sato transform of a cuspidal perverse sheaf is cuspidal, we see that",
